<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.254438>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Automate dolichognatha De Man, 1888: A—ovigerous female (cl 4.4 mm) from Tanjung Aan, Lombok, Indonesia (RMNH. CRUS. D. 56741), dorsolateral view (minor cheliped missing); B—specimen (cl 3.4 mm, sex not determinable) from the same locality (MZB Cru 4046), dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/254438/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

